Package org.apache.hadoop.io.compress.zlib

Class Summary
BuiltInZlibDeflater A wrapper around java.util.zip.Deflater to make it conform to org.apache.hadoop.io.compress.Compressor interface.
BuiltInZlibInflater A wrapper around java.util.zip.Inflater to make it conform to org.apache.hadoop.io.compress.Decompressor interface.
ZlibCompressor A Compressor based on the popular zlib compression algorithm.
ZlibDecompressor A Decompressor based on the popular zlib compression algorithm.
ZlibFactory A collection of factories to create the right zlib/gzip compressor/decompressor instances.
 

Enum Summary
ZlibCompressor.CompressionHeader The type of header for compressed data.
ZlibCompressor.CompressionLevel The compression level for zlib library.
ZlibCompressor.CompressionStrategy The compression level for zlib library.
ZlibDecompressor.CompressionHeader The headers to detect from compressed data.
